#: ../../source/reference/tensor/generated/maxframe.tensor.nanstd.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.tensor.nanstd"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:1 of
msgid ""
"Compute the standard deviation along the specified axis, while ignoring "
"NaNs."
msgstr "计算沿指定轴的标准差，同时忽略 NaN。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:4 of
msgid ""
"Returns the standard deviation, a measure of the spread of a "
"distribution, of the non-NaN tensor elements. The standard deviation is "
"computed for the flattened tensor by default, otherwise over the "
"specified axis."
msgstr ""
"返回非 NaN tensor 元素的标准差，即分布的离散程度。默认情况下计算展平后的 "
"tensor 的标准差，否则在指定轴上计算。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:9 of
msgid ""
"For all-NaN slices or slices with zero degrees of freedom, NaN is "
"returned and a `RuntimeWarning` is raised."
msgstr ""
"对于全为 NaN 的切片或自由度为零的切片，返回 NaN 并发出 `RuntimeWarning` "
"警告。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:12 of
msgid "Calculate the standard deviation of the non-NaN values."
msgstr "计算非 NaN 值的标准差。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:14 of
msgid ""
"Axis along which the standard deviation is computed. The default is to "
"compute the standard deviation of the flattened tensor."
msgstr "计算标准差的轴。默认计算展平后的 tensor 的标准差。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:17 of
msgid ""
"Type to use in computing the standard deviation. For tensors of integer "
"type the default is float64, for tensors of float types it is the same as"
" the tensor type."
msgstr ""
"计算标准差时使用的类型。对于整数类型的 tensor，默认为 float64，对于浮点"
"类型的 tensor 则与 tensor 类型相同。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:21 of
msgid ""
"Alternative output tensor in which to place the result. It must have the "
"same shape as the expected output but the type (of the calculated values)"
" will be cast if necessary."
msgstr ""
"用于存放结果的替代输出 tensor。它必须与预期输出具有相同的形状，但类型（"
"计算值的类型）在必要时会被转换。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:25 of
msgid ""
"Means Delta Degrees of Freedom.  The divisor used in calculations is ``N "
"- ddof``, where ``N`` represents the number of non-NaN elements.  By "
"default `ddof` is zero."
msgstr ""
"表示 Delta 自由度。计算时使用的除数是 ``N - ddof``，其中 ``N`` 表示非 NaN"
" 元素的数量。默认 `ddof` 为 0。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:29 of
msgid ""
"If this is set to True, the axes which are reduced are left in the result"
" as dimensions with size one. With this option, the result will broadcast"
" correctly against the original `a`.  If this value is anything but the "
"default it is passed through as-is to the relevant functions of the sub-"
"classes.  If these functions do not have a `keepdims` kwarg, a "
"RuntimeError will be raised."
msgstr ""
"如果设置为 True，则在结果中保留被缩减的轴，其大小为 1。使用此选项时，结果"
"将能正确广播到原始 `a`。如果该值不是默认值，则会原样传递给子类的相关函数"
"。如果这些函数没有 `keepdims` 参数，则会引发 RuntimeError。"

#: maxframe.tensor.reduction.nanstd.nanstd:29 of
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
